title: 703. Breaking Down Hall of Fame Induction Ceremonies
itunes:title: 703. Breaking Down Hall of Fame Induction Ceremonies
description:
Bucky Brooks is back with a new episode of Move the Sticks with special guest Steve Wyche. On this show, the guys look at the players, coaches and contributors that were inducted into the Hall of Fame this past weekend. To wrap up the show, the pair discuss the situation surrounding Texans quarterback Deshaun Watson in Houston.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
